name: JewelDefactaPastel11
description:
JewelDefactaPastel11 is a model Merged PastelMix and Defacta11, and I trained it with my AI art training set, and then mixed PastelMix another time.

Working good with PastelMix's vae, but none vae is good too.

bad-artist and bad-hands-5, badhandv4, EasyNegative etc is working good.


Here's my twitter! Please follow me and share me your art!

https://twitter.com/FireWaterAgate

Defacta

https://civitai.com/models/23804/defacta

PastelMix

https://civitai.com/models/5414/pastel-mix-stylized-anime-model-fantasyai
